description: Bian Dang is yummy Taiwanese street food! Formerly known as NYC Cravings Bian Dang: Taiwanese Rice Box What to Eat?Try the Taiwanese style fried chicken or pork over rice with pork sauce, the Taiwanese style fried tianbula (fish cake) over rice with pork sauce, the four pieces of pork dumplings, or the Zongzi (Chinese tamale).To learn more about Bian Dang and their delicious secret recipe, check out the Roaming Hunger interview with them here: http://roaminghunger.com/blog/4406/featured-food-truck-bian-dang
name: Bian Dang
